tnote.parser

Class TNotesParserQuery

  • java.lang.Object
    • tnote.parser.TNotesParserQuery

  • public class TNotesParserQuery
extends java.lang.Object
    This class manages all the checking in the input String. It will indicate whether a particular word is in the sentence. It retrieves the necessary information about tasks and returns it to the UI class
